{"tid":1067344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"𡃁模張欣欣YanyanC回應投訴餐廳事件！","createTime":"2019-03-18T12:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T14:38:00.000Z","uid":51464,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6eaf113ae9d18155ce6d9b0a7b4f75bd6a2542a6","tid":1067344,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"雖然「The Beggar in the Restaurant 乞客」Facebook 專頁未有公開涉及投訴的客人名字，但網民已從 IG Stories 的相關擷圖中，得悉其中 1 位相關客人是女模特兒張欣欣（YanyanC，Yanyan Cheung），其 IG 帳號的 Followers 數目約為 87,900。事件中，餐廳職員所提供的服務，確實存有一定問題。不過，多數網民認為張欣欣及其友人的投訴「去得太盡」，亦令到涉事的侍應有機會失去工作，普遍傾向支持餐廳和侍應。部分網民更在張欣欣的 Facebook 專頁和 Instagram 帳號留下大量負面留言，迫使張欣欣的 Instagram 帳號開啟了限制留言功能，及後張欣欣更曾一度將個人 Instagram 帳號內的全部相片和影片隱藏起來。<br />\n<br />\n在 3 月 18 日晚上，張欣欣在 Instagram Stories 回應事件，並上傳了跟餐廳代表通話的電話錄音，餐廳代表明確表示事件中的餐廳侍應仍未被解雇。張欣欣亦表示她僅在其 IG Stories 上，投訴相關餐廳服務不周，其餘投訴都是她的友人所為。她在宣泄情緒不滿後，當晚已刪除了 IG Stories 上的投訴內容。對於今次事件，張欣欣為個人衝動行為，以及為事件做成的不便致歉，她願意作出任何解釋及協助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2300174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2300174&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=4c8dc267\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2300174</a><br />\n=============================<br />\nIn 閨蜜 we trust！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5edda9ec3a3a92a6551f35815e7bb4f43f1083","tid":1067344,"uid":223016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"On"},{"pid":"895ea9d3727cee0d99e4c58d276f3985dc76aa45","tid":1067344,"uid":223016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:46:28.000Z